            <who name="Fabian Jakobs">fabian.jakobs</who>
            <bug_when>2007-04-17 10:29:19 +0200</bug_when>
            <thetext>A new property &quot;liveUpdate&quot; was added. If live update is set to true, the value property is updated on each &quot;input&quot; event. This makes the method &quot;getComputedValue&quot; obsolete.

The class has been documented to avoid further confusion.</thetext>
